_sText:
To install follow these steps:

1: Go to your steam file. (exapample:   C:/programs/steam)

2: steamapps > (your steam account name) > counter-strike source > cstrike > maps

Put the NAV-file and BSP-file in the maps folder and then your ready to play.


Map created by SemperIdem 
- OFcgaming.com

Enjoy!

Seriously if you have downloaded and played the map DO NOT forget to comment!!
